body.text: The ICT Competition 2024-2025 roadshow has been buzzing across campuses, connecting with students and spreading the word about this exciting opportunity. The video from the Multimedia University of Kenya shows just how vibrant the event has been. It’s a great chance to get involved, learn, and showcase what you can do. If you're passionate about tech or looking to improve your skills, this competition seems like a good place to start.

discoverable_identity_badges_web.information_description: 超级粉丝是因为与公共主页或个人主页互动最积极而获得徽章的用户。这枚徽章会在他们评论时显示，从而对其积极性表示赞赏。
这些用户因为与 Huawei  Kenya 互动积极而获得徽章，再进一步就可成为超级粉丝。这枚徽章会在他们评论时显示，从而对其积极性表示赞赏。
